snippet.title: Halloween is Coming: Oliver and Mom Trick or Treat Preparations
snippet.description:
Oliver and Mom are preparing for Halloween. From putting up a banner to picking out the perfect costumes, they're all ready to go! Diana and Roma join them on Trick or Treat Adventure. It's sure to be a Halloween to remember!

Whether you're a Halloween fan or not, this video is sure to be loads of fun!

Thanks for watching!
